  "instructions": [
    "Heat 2 tablespoons of vegetable oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add minced garlic and ginger and sauté for 1 minute.",
    "Add sliced mushrooms, bell peppers, and onion. Cook until the vegetables are tender.",
    "Stir in hot chilli powder, fish sauce, soy sauce, and lime juice.",
    "Add cooked Thai Jasmine Rice to the skillet and stir-fry for 2-3 minutes.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning with salt and black pepper.",
    "Transfer the rice mixture to a serving bowl and garnish with chopped cilantro and sliced green chilli (if using).",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!"
